**********************************************************************
Build methods as follows:
Method A:
	1. cd mtv_50 

	2. make buildall

	then, you can get boot.bin loader.bin minios.bin

Method B:
	1. cd mtv_50 

	2. make build_boot
		you can get boot.bin

	3. make build_minios
		you can get minios.bin

	4. make build_loader
		you can get loader.bin

Clean methods:
	1. make cleanall
		make clean for boot, minios and loader

	2. make clean_boot
		make clean for boot

	3. make clean_minios
		make clean for minios

	4. make clean_loader
		make clean for loader
